<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Termination Notice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #dc3545;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .notice-box {
            background-color: #fff3f3;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Termination Notice</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
            
            <div class="notice-box">
                <p>We regret to inform you that your counselor account with MiCounselor has been terminated.</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Reason for Termination:</strong></p>
            <p><%= reason %></p>

            <p>As a result of this termination:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your access to the MiCounselor platform has been revoked</li>
                <li>Your profile has been removed from our directory</li>
                <li>All scheduled sessions have been cancelled</li>
                <li>Your account data will be handled according to our data retention policy</li>
            </ul>

            <p>If you believe this decision was made in error or would like to appeal, please contact our support team within 7 days.</p>

            <p>Thank you for your service with MiCounselor.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The MiCounselor Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MiCounselor. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>For support, please contact: support@micounselor.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>